<br>
I would say PoP is definately worth it, you will have access to Innovation, Disease and Nightmare without the need for flags (Justice too, but people don't seem to want to group there). The exp in these zones is far superior to other zones and, being a wizard, you should be able to get into trials groups easier than my paladin.  <br>
<br>
