Well, exp is much lower in other areas compared to pop already. Most of the tier one planes I see are filled with people in their 50's to level up. It is a much easier route than doing xp without using pop.<br>
<br>
Don't be scared of levelling up to 60 and beyond here. Maybe get 61 or 62. You should also find these spells pretty cheap in the bazaar. Its ok to let people know what your situation is, and guilds with a mature attitude (ie, known as ubers to some, known as famliy guilds to others) will accept and work with you.<br>
<br>
